Dia. 01 If White Plays it is Sente
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is sente if White plays hane and connects with 1 and 3.
\par
\par Black has to defend at 4.
\par So if White plays, it is sente, but on the contrary, Black played hane and connected at 1 and 3 in the previous diagram. Black has removed White's privilage, which makes the value big.
\par }
