Dia. 03 The Value of Hane and Connection
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Let's check the value of this sequence.
\par It is a bit difficult, but it is necessary to know the way of counting.
\par
\par The borderlines are made for convenient counting.
\par So White has 6 points and Black has 7 points inside the Xs.
\par
\par
\par }
