Dia. 04 Counting
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par This is the shape when White played hane and connected.
\par This time the borderlines are made with Xs again.
\par
\par White has 7 points and Black has 5 points inside the Xs.
\par
\par After counting it is
\par (7\'a3\'ad6)\'a3\'ab(7\'a3\'ad5)\'a3\'bd3 points.
\par
\par The value of Black's hane and connection is \cf1\b 3 points\cf0\b0 . (Same for White's hane and connection)
\par }
